00:35:17.070 --> 00:35:17.860
Speak.

00:35:17.880 --> 00:35:18.570
What is it?

00:35:21.480 --> 00:35:22.340
His Majesty ordered me

00:35:22.550 --> 00:35:24.050
to bring you the Phoenix Seal

00:35:24.150 --> 00:35:25.780
and say you will always be Empress of Great Qi.

00:35:26.630 --> 00:35:28.570
Have you ever seen an empress who walked away from the palace?

00:35:28.860 --> 00:35:32.020
♪Gently to the night sky

