♪I'm swept into the endless torrent...♪

00:36:03.360 --> 00:36:04.130
Your Majesty,

00:36:04.760 --> 00:36:05.780
it's time for your medicine.

00:36:06.510 --> 00:36:07.460
Leave it there for now.

00:36:10.110 --> 00:36:11.170
The situation at the front is complicated.

00:36:11.840 --> 00:36:13.490
There's no need to press yourself.

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:15.650
Please take care of your health.

00:36:17.280 --> 00:36:18.340
I know what I'm doing.

00:36:18.710 --> 00:36:19.690
You may go.

00:36:31.540 --> 00:36:33.940
♪Falling petals♪

00:36:34.860 --> 00:36:38.020
♪Petals drifting through the sky...♪

00:36:40.920 --> 00:36:41.530
Your Majesty.

00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:45.860
Is she all right?

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:48.610
The Empress slipped into the westbound relief army.

00:36:48.670 --> 00:36:49.490
She's fine for now.

